author: Christina Carrega
title: 70 people contract coronavirus in San Francisco's largest homeless shelter
description: Advocates are calling out officials for not placing homeless in shelters sooner.
content:
At one of the largest homeless shelters in San Francisco, California, 70 people tested positive for thecoronavirus, officials said.
